                                    </a>
                                </div> -->
                  <div class="p-card-description">
                    <h2 class="text-dark">Arcane Ops. Paranormal Podcast.</h2>
                    <div class="hr-div"></div>
                    <p class="text-dark"> 
                      Arcane Ops was a limited-run paranormal podcast that ran for seven episodes at the end of 2020. I designed the layout in Adobe XD and built it using WordPress, WooCommerce, and Bootstrap. All logos and graphics were designed in Adobe CC.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-dark small">
                      WordPress, HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Bootstrap, Adobe CC
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- End individual portfolio card -->
            <!-- Start individual portfolio card -->
            <div class="carousel-item">
              <div class="row d-flex align-items-center p-card-container">
                <!-- Card image -->
                <div class="p-card-img-div">
                  <img src="img/corporate-law-homepage.webp" class="img-fluid" alt="Homepage for corporate law website, built using Webflow." />
                </div>
                <!-- Card description -->
                <div class="p-card-caption">
